\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 THE STORY OF BORDER CORNER}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Nearly two years have passed since the Alliance and the Horde laid siege to Hellfire Citadel \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u226\'E2\u8364\'80\u8220\'93 the heart of the Burning Legion's power \u226\'E2\u8364\'80\u8220\'93 and the war that followed has seen the heroes of the Horde and Alliance enter a new phase of their conflict.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 While the war in eastern Plaguelands has seen great valor on the part of both sides, an equally great effort has been made to minimize casualties amongst the ranks of both factions. As such, the level of combat in the war has been gradually lowered over time \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u226\'E2\u8364\'80\u8220\'93 gradually opening the way for a possible future New Azeroth!}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 DARKFRONT}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The High Warlord Kil'jaeden has forged an accord with the Witch-King Azeroth to lead the way against the Legion. The Alliance has agreed to aid the war effort, while the Legion has been folded into the War on Terror. The two factions will now each lead a wing of a wing that will attack the enemy capital \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u226\'E2\u8364\'80\u8220\'93 the exact location of this new Nagrand raid dungeon has yet to be confirmed.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
