\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Nagrand has been added to the game world as a fully-fledged zone with a number of new features, including an exclusive dungeon for Legion, a new chapter of the War on Terror expansion that is set in Nagrand, and a raid-style version of the raid dungeon, all of which can be attempted at level 80. In addition to the dungeon and raid sections, Nagrand also features a faction-based aspect, meaning players can visit their faction-based counterparts to obtain the requisite reputation to challenge them \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u226\'E2\u8364\'80\u8220\'93 all of these efforts will be at no additional cost.}
