\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0  * Priest Bug Fixes}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0     * Casting a cleansing or calming spell while a party member is afflicted by [Mind Flay]'s [Seal of Insight] effect shouldn't cause combat pet abilities to trigger Innervate, [Divine Hymn], or [Divine Steed] (the targeted pet should no longer be highlighted under the appropriate UI).}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0     * Casting [Power Word: Shield] while under the affects of [Mind Spike] should no longer cause the Priest to be stuck with the Power Word: Shield effect that's already active.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0     * The [Guardian Spirit] talent can no longer be used to remove movement impairing effects that interfere with receiving a shield.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0     * Warning: [Divine Aegis] can no longer be cast while [Divine Hymn] is already active.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0     * Stealing damage with [Prayer of Mending] should no longer cause the Priest's [Mind Sear] ability to trigger a cooldown for Mind Sear.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0     * The [Shackle Undead] effect of the Priest's spell [Mind Rip] is now properly considered a Snare.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0     * Casting [Surge of Light] while [Shadow Word: Pain] is already on the target should no longer cause the Surge of Light effect to be removed without benefit.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0     * Surge of Light has a 0.75 second cast time, and its duration has been reduced to 12 seconds (was 15 seconds).}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0     *  [Surge of Light] triggers immediately after [Mind Spike] and before any other movement enhancing effect (was 3 seconds).}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0     *  [Shackle Undead] will now provide a +15% damage bonus to [Prayer of Mending] and [Guardian Spirit] to help compensate for it taking longer to cast.}
